Being a nanny with my age and experience seems appropriate, because I love children and I am more patient without having lost vitality.  It allows me to put in practice some of the knowledge I have gathered, as well as to create more lasting affective ties. In my work, I conciliate the feeling of home, with professional responsibilities.

